um.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2747, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Coast_(New_South_Wales)\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NSW Central Coast\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Coast_(New_South_Wales)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_Coast_(New_South_Wales)\"}, {\"begin\": 2773, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Terrigal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.564939984474785e-16, \"text\": \"Terrigal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Terrigal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electoral_district_of_Terrigal\"}, {\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"score\": 0.9999990496071374, \"rank\": 9.500489072720514e-07, \"text\": \"Molly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rising charger\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is currently ranked fourth in the world and attributes some of her success to her local surfing environment.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"her success\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"her local surfing environment\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picklum is one of a group of young female surfers to have burst onto the scene in recent years, surfing waves of consequence at such high levels they are drawing attention away from the traditional male domination in the sport.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picklum\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 29